<h3>Summary</h3>

<p>
ABM Warranty supports multiple sync types so teams can choose the right scope
for routine maintenance, broad refreshes, or targeted troubleshooting. Each
mode aligns to a specific operational intent and provides a predictable path for
running sync jobs in managed environments.
